14 c. Service pursuant to this paragraph shall be made by
15 publication of a notice, signed by the court clerk,
16 one (1) day a week for three (3) consecutive weeks in
17 a newspaper authorized by law to publish legal notices
18 which is published in the county where the petition is
19 filed. If no newspaper authorized by law to publish
