5 punishable by imprisonment in the county jail for not more than one
6 (1) year, by a fine not to exceed One Thousand Dollars ($1,000.00),
7 or by both such imprisonment and fine.
8 B. Every person who commits any battery or assault and battery
9 upon any county commissioner, county clerk, county assessor, county
10 treasurer, or officer of a state district or appellate court, or the
